text: The 2005 Georgia Southern Eagles football team represented the Georgia Southern Eagles of Georgia Southern University during the 2005 NCAA Division I-AA football season. The Eagles played their home games at Paulson Stadium in Statesboro, Georgia. The team was coached by Mike Sewak, in his fourth and final year as head coach for the Eagles. ==Schedule== ==References== Georgia Southern Category:Georgia Southern Eagles football seasons Georgia Southern Eagles football
